{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-help-a-coworker-troubleshoot-on-github/task-48","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-help-a-coworker-troubleshoot-on-github","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Poslušaj zvuk i odgovori na pitanje.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-help-a-coworker-troubleshoot-on-github/task-48"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta planira da uradi Sara, i kako veruje da će to pomoći?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Planira da ispravi PR i veruje da će to rešiti problem odjednom.</p>","feedback":"<p>Plan Sarah je da kreira novi PR sa <em>rollback</em>-om, ne samo da popravi postojeći PR, i nadaju se da će to pomoći u otkrivanju problema.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Planira da obriše PR i veruje da će to otkriti problem.</p>","feedback":"<p>Umesto brisanja, Sarah planira da kreira novi PR za popravku grešaka, sa ciljem otkrivanja problema.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kreira novi PR sa rollback-om i dodatnim logovima, ili naiđe na problem.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Želi da se konsultuje sa timom, misleći da mogu brzo da reše problem.</p>","feedback":"<p>Sarahin hitni plan je kreirati PR, a ne konsultovati se sa timom za sada.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Sarah","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"6.1-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":25.18,"finishTimestamp":31.76},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity"